1063
01:09:13,002 --> 01:09:15,002
S.H.I.E.L.D. Monitors potential threats.

1064
01:09:15,002 --> 01:09:16,420
Captain America's on threat watch?

1065
01:09:16,421 --> 01:09:17,546
We all are.

1066
01:09:17,546 --> 01:09:19,090
Wait, you're on that list?

1067
01:09:19,091 --> 01:09:20,757
Are you above or below angry bees?

1068
01:09:20,759 --> 01:09:22,881
Stark, so help me God,
if you make one more wisecrack...

1069
01:09:23,011 --> 01:09:24,386
Threat! Verbal threat. I feel threatened.

1070
01:09:24,387 --> 01:09:26,878
- Show some respect.
- Respect what?

1071
01:09:34,231 --> 01:09:37,149
<i>Transport Six-Six-Bravo,
please relay confirm codes.</i>

1072
01:09:37,277 --> 01:09:39,435
<i>I've got you on the computer,
but not on the day log.</i>

1073
01:09:39,570 --> 01:09:41,645
<i>What is your haul? Over.</i>

1074
01:09:41,780 --> 01:09:44,402
<i>Arms and ammunition. Over.</i>

1075
01:09:52,751 --> 01:09:54,957
You speak of control,
yet you court chaos.

1076
01:09:55,087 --> 01:09:56,921
That's his M.O., isn't it?

1077
01:09:56,921 --> 01:09:58,296
I mean, what are we, a team?

1078
01:09:58,297 --> 01:10:01,252
No, we're a chemical mixture
that makes chaos.

1079
01:10:01,385 --> 01:10:03,385
We're a time bomb.

1080
01:10:03,470 --> 01:10:05,430
You need to step away.

1081
01:10:05,430 --> 01:10:07,390
Why shouldn't the guy
let off a little steam?

1082
01:10:07,390 --> 01:10:09,512
You know damn well why. Back off!

1083
01:10:09,643 --> 01:10:11,849
I'm starting to want you to make me.

1084
01:10:11,979 --> 01:10:15,596
Yeah. Big man in a suit of armour.

1085
01:10:15,733 --> 01:10:17,317
Take that off, what are you?

1086
01:10:17,318 --> 01:10:19,643
Genius, billionaire,
playboy, philanthropist.

1087
01:10:20,529 --> 01:10:23,695
I know guys with none of that
worth ten of you.

1088
01:10:23,824 --> 01:10:24,949
I've seen the footage.

1089
01:10:24,951 --> 01:10:27,193
The only thing you really
fight for is yourself.

1090
