1118
01:12:15,480 --> 01:12:17,480
Got it.

1119
01:12:17,484 --> 01:12:18,609
Sorry, kids,

1120
01:12:18,609 --> 01:12:20,485
you don't get to see
my party trick after all.

1121
01:12:20,487 --> 01:12:21,612
You located the Tesseract?

1122
01:12:21,613 --> 01:12:22,738
