1123
01:12:22,738 --> 01:12:24,860
The Tesseract belongs on Asgard.
No human is a match for it.

1124
01:12:24,990 --> 01:12:26,449
- You're not going alone.
- You're gonna stop me?

1125
01:12:26,451 --> 01:12:27,576
Put on the suit, let's find out.

1126
01:12:27,577 --> 01:12:28,993
I'm not afraid to hit an old man.

1127
01:12:28,994 --> 01:12:30,994
Put on the suit.

1128
01:12:32,873 --> 01:12:34,873
Oh, my God.

1129
01:12:50,016 --> 01:12:51,141
Put on the suit.

1130
01:12:51,143 --> 01:12:53,143
Yeah.

1131
01:12:55,189 --> 01:12:57,189
<i>All hands to stations.</i>

