1168
01:15:35,645 --> 01:15:37,851
- Yes, sir.
- Then put it on the left.

1169
01:15:37,980 --> 01:15:39,774
Get us over water.

1170
01:15:39,774 --> 01:15:41,850
One more turbine goes down,
