1194
01:18:02,922 --> 01:18:04,465
long enough to disengage
maglev and that could...

1195
01:18:04,466 --> 01:18:06,466
Speak English!

1196
01:18:07,136 --> 01:18:09,136
You see that red lever?

1197
01:18:09,555 --> 01:18:11,677
<i>It will slow the rotors down
long enough for me to get out.</i>

1198
01:18:11,806 --> 01:18:13,806
Stand by it. Wait for my word.

