1205
01:19:42,734 --> 01:19:44,400
<i>Levels 2 and 3 are dark.</i>

1206
01:19:44,402 --> 01:19:46,524
Sir, the Hulk will tear this place apart!

1207
01:19:47,738 --> 01:19:48,863
Get his attention.

1208
01:19:48,864 --> 01:19:53,029
Escort 6-0, proceed to
Wishbone and engage hostile.

1209
01:19:53,162 --> 01:19:54,578
<i>Don't get too close.</i>

1210
01:19:54,579 --> 01:19:56,579
<i>Copy.</i>

1211
01:20:07,885 --> 01:20:09,885
<i>Target acquired.</i>

1212
01:20:13,556 --> 01:20:15,556
<i>Target engaged.</i>

1213
01:20:26,195 --> 01:20:28,195
<i>Target angry, target angry!</i>

1214
01:21:36,141 --> 01:21:38,349
They're not getting through
here, so what the hell...

1215
01:21:56,747 --> 01:21:58,988
<i>Engine one is now in shut-down.</i>

1216
01:22:07,425 --> 01:22:09,582
We are in an uncontrolled descent.

1217
01:22:09,719 --> 01:22:11,719
<i>Sir, we've lost all power in engine one.</i>

1218
01:22:12,137 --> 01:22:14,097
<i>It's Barton. He took out our systems.</i>

1219
01:22:14,099 --> 01:22:16,590
<i>He's headed for the detention level.</i>

1220
01:22:16,725 --> 01:22:18,725
<i>Does anybody copy?</i>

1221
01:22:19,854 --> 01:22:21,976
This is Agent Romanoff.

1222
01:22:22,105 --> 01:22:24,105
I copy.

1223
01:22:28,195 --> 01:22:29,320
<i>Stark, we're losing altitude.</i>

1224
01:22:29,322 --> 01:22:31,322
Yeah, I noticed.

1225
01:22:59,811 --> 01:23:01,811
No!

1226
01:23:08,445 --> 01:23:11,150
Are you ever not going to fall for that?

1227
01:23:54,159 --> 01:23:56,402
The humans think us immortal.

1228
01:23:57,497 --> 01:23:59,497
Should we test that?

1229
01:24:01,835 --> 01:24:03,835
Move away, please.

1230
01:24:07,506 --> 01:24:09,506
You like this?

1231
01:24:09,966 --> 01:24:13,217
We started working on the prototype
after you sent the Destroyer.

1232
01:24:14,430 --> 01:24:16,671
