1233
01:24:17,475 --> 01:24:19,475
Do you want to find out?

1234
01:24:20,729 --> 01:24:22,729
No!

1235
01:25:31,717 --> 01:25:33,717
Natasha?

1236
01:26:04,711 --> 01:26:06,711
You're going to lose.

1237
01:26:08,506 --> 01:26:10,506
Am I?

1238
01:26:11,009 --> 01:26:13,500
It's in your nature.

1239
01:26:15,680 --> 01:26:18,006
Your heroes are scattered.

1240
01:26:18,141 --> 01:26:21,842
Your floating fortress falls from the sky.

1241
01:26:21,979 --> 01:26:23,979
Where is my disadvantage?

1242
01:26:24,271 --> 01:26:26,349
You lack conviction.

1243
01:26:27,192 --> 01:26:29,192
I don't think I'm...

1244
01:26:35,033 --> 01:26:37,033
So, that's what it does.

1245
01:26:38,829 --> 01:26:41,949
<i>All hands
to crash stations immediately.</i>

1246
01:27:09,569 --> 01:27:10,944
Cap, hit the lever.

1247
01:27:10,945 --> 01:27:13,520
