1253
01:28:08,046 --> 01:28:09,631
Just stay awake.

1254
01:28:09,631 --> 01:28:11,381
Eyes on me.

1255
01:28:11,382 --> 01:28:13,050
No, I'm clocking out here.

1256
01:28:13,051 --> 01:28:15,051
Not an option.

1257
